---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import chefPortrait from "../../assets/images/chef-portrait.jpg";
---

<section class="py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a] text-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2
        class="font-(family-name:--font-playfair) text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4"
      >
        Meet Our Chef
      </h2>
      <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-[#d4af37] mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-100 justify-items-center"
    >
      <!-- Chef Image -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div class="relative h-160 w-80 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <Image
            src={chefPortrait}
            alt="Chef Michel Beaumont"
            class="object-cover w-full h-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Chef Bio -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
            Chef Michel Beaumont
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#d4af37] font-semibold text-sm">Chef & Founder</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed">
          With over 25 years of culinary experience, Chef Michel Beaumont has
          trained under some of the world's most renowned Michelin-starred
          chefs. His innovative approach to classical French cuisine has earned
          Epicure recognition and accolades from prestigious culinary guides.
        </p>

        <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Chef Michel's philosophy centers on respecting the ingredient,
          honoring tradition while embracing innovation, and creating dishes
          that tell a story. His passion for excellence extends beyond the
          kitchen—he believes that hospitality and genuine care for guests are
          essential to the dining experience.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-2 pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm! text-[#a0a0a0]">
            <strong>Education:</strong> Le Cordon Bleu, Paris
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm! text-[#a0a0a0]">
            <strong>Experience:</strong> Former sous chef at Restaurant L'Astrance,
            Paris
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm! text-[#a0a0a0]">
            <strong>Specialties:</strong> French cuisine, seasonal cooking, sustainable
            ingredients
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
